    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Equipment for children's playgrounds or other venues, comprising a flat disk suspended on a pole in the middle, with bars for hand-holds and support; the devices spin using manual rotary motion supplied by a child or adult pushing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
